title: Apple iPad Air 10.5-inch
description: This Apple iPad Air has a 10.5-inch display with 1668 x 2224 pixel resolution (~265 pixels per inch). Powered by Apple A12 Bionic chipset, Hexa-Core processor, and Apple GPU. Storage capacity of 64GB with 3GB of RAM for memory. The main camera is 8.0 megapixels. This device is also Wi-Fi Only. Comes in Original Box and bundle includes Case, Tempered Glass, Stylus Pen, Bluetooth Headset, and Rapid Charger! This device has been tested to be in great working condition. It will show signs of use and cosmetic blemishes which may included some scratched/dings, all of which do not affect the usability of this device. (Refurbished)

title: Apple 11-inch iPad Pro
description: Apple 11-inch iPad Pro (2021) Wifi 2TB-Space Gray iPad Pro features the powerful Apple M1 chip with next-level performance and all-day battery life. The Liquid Retina display on the 11-inch iPad Pro is not only gorgeous, but super portable. And a front camera with Center Stage keeps you in frame automatically during video calls. iPad Pro has pro cameras and a LiDAR Scanner for stunning photos, videos, and immersive AR. Thunderbolt for connecting to high-performance accessories and you can add Apple Pencil for note-taking, drawing, and marking up documents, and the Magic Keyboard for a responsive typing experience and trackpad.

title: Lenovo Tab M10 Plus
description: The Lenovo Tab M10 Plus (3rd Gen) pushes the boundaries of what's possible for tablet-based multimedia entertainment with a stunning 10" FHD TDDI IPS display that features two-sided narrow borders, upgraded octa-core processors and all-day battery life.
